Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Marineford is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:37.86,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Absolute Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.60,0:04:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's willing to destroy the whole island!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna leave you! You gotta come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you disobey your Captain's order?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just go, fools?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is our chance!\NKill Whitebeard! He's dying already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Let's do as Pops said!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mind leaving Pops behind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, how dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid! No one wants to leave him alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Grumbling about it at a time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,like this is the same as trampling on Pops' determination!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and get ready to sail out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna leave soon! Come on now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Marco, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You messed with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! All I want is to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My wax is as strong as steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that a normal sword can cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's also a Devil Fruit user!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's strong enough to try to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.07,0:06:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Fist even at Fleet Admiral Sengoku's elbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No no, don't overestimate me like that! I'm not a big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he still has that much power\Nafter getting wounded so badly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he isn't concerned\Nabout Fire Fist Ace anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fleet Admiral Sengoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's clear his intention is to sink Marineford into the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Along with himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Admiral Garp! You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to end this era? Yeah, the time is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Whitebeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:08:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Were his allies defeated after he sold them out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the connection still out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How long should we wait?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! We couldn't see the whole picture
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,because Buggy the Clown stood in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.88,0:08:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy over there must be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The great pirate—Captain Buggy the Clown?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's who I am indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he want to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If nothing is done, I can't report anything to the head office!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on at Marineford now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Transponder Snail hasn't come out yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Captain Buggy is about to\Nbeat Whitebeard—it's no time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say it as if it's so easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dying but he still has\Nboundless power—didn't they see it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:09:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I even say that I'm gonna beat that man?! I really screwed this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it! It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! We gotta broadcast Captain Buggy's\Nbig moment all over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it out at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Or we're gonna burn you out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we gotta soak it into water!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:23.28,Alt,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like he volunteered to be a slave for the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But he got beaten up in the battlefield like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel sorry for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let him go, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we gotta cancel\N"Captain Buggy's beating Whitebeard
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and broadcast it live to the world" plan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Even you want to pull out from Marineford?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm disappointed in you, Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:09:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes down to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,they're all strong guys\Nwho've been locked up in Impel Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I better not make enemies of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The Transponder Snail came out voluntarily!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! He came out because he was touched\Nby Captain Buggy's kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Buggy can even win the hearts of the Snails!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's amazing as we thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the man who will conquer the world—he's our Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn bastard! Why didn't he just stay inside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now there's no way that I can back out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Buggy, make a declaration to conquer the world now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoke: good, lighting: good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand by!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I mean... Dammit! This leaves me one choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, shoot my bravery!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Capture the moment that I kill Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The picture's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't see what's going on\Nbecause of the smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the Navy losing?!\NWhat happened to Whitebeard and Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Transponder Snail, go lower!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, everyone! I'm Buggy and I'm a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to the sea now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Those remaining have to get back\Nto the New World safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them get away! Kill as many as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one that you ought to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Jozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's badly injured but he'll make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.64,0:12:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain gave us an order! Come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Brenheim! You gotta carry Jozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:11.98,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Straw-boy! Why are you standing around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, let's go! The old man has made up his mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! And it won't be in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.86,0:12:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Back off, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need words now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you happy to have me as your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Still some fight left in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You are too valuable to let die now, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you still wanna run wild, run as wild as you want on the sea under my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:13:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Become my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The scaffold was destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So was Navy HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Ace get executed?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Move the camera to Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Buggy and I'm a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.62,0:15:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The great pirate—Captain Buggy the Clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that you're gonna beat Whitebeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And with his head in your hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you're willing to become one of the Four Emperors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Buggy and I'm a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just repeating that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something forward-looking! Let's do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough with Buggy already!\NShow us what's going on in Marineford!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not what we're interested in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean... I just wanna do something flashy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Run to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace-san, Luffy-kun, get in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:52.07,Alt,,0,0,0,,Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to get you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But what the old chap wants\Nis as many survivors as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We've stolen a Navy ship! Get on board quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they really think that they can get away?!\NHow simple they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Admiral Sakazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys, move aside a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You two, just keep going until you get to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as you rescue Fire Fist Ace,\Nyou start running!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Whitebeards must be a group of cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's obviously trying to provoke you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stop, you're playing right into his hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well your captain is that kind of guy\Nso you can't help it, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:17:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Because after all, Whitebeard is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,... a loser from a bygone era!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A loser?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Take back what you just said!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't, Ace! Don't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let him say whatever he wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He mocked Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.47,0:17:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say "take it back?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in a million years! I'll tell you why.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father Gold Roger conquered the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and opened the door to the new era called
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the Great Pirate Era by sacrificing himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,As a Navy admiral, it's not my place to say so,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but he was true to his name: the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In contrast, what has Whitebeard done?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he really had the intention to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume that he established a large family someplace
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and was satisfied being a big fish in a little barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some fools in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,who'd say that his name\Nis keeping peace on various islands
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you ask me,\Nhe's just intimidating small-fry
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and thinks that makes him a hero. Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When Roger was alive, Whitebeard had second billing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and even after Roger's death, he couldn't become King.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That means he'll never surpass Roger.\NHe'll be a loser forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's who Whitebeard is and that's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a poor man when you think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He gathered some punks who call him Pops
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:18:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and roamed the sea with his fake family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:19:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Although he reigned over the sea for decades,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,he couldn't become the King and attained nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, he was stabbed by a fool—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,one of his own sons—who fell for my lie
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and he will die to protect that foolish son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.51,0:19:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that's an empty existence?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Ace, come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops gave us a place to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't understand his greatness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.73,0:19:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,People don't deserve to live if they can't live justly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Punks like you guys don't deserve a place to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Whitebeard will die as a loser!\NIt's fitting for a big fish in a little barrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.68,0:20:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whitebeard is a great pirate who shaped this era!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make fun of the man who saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The name of this era should be "Whitebeard!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Whitebeard and you guys who call him Pops
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.84,0:20:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,are the same after all—losers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace has been burned!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.23,0:20:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you careless because you ate a Logia type fruit which
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is the most powerful of all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just fire but my magma can even burn fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.51,0:20:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My power is far stronger than yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy-kun, you shouldn't fight anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace's Vivre Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger the Pirate King. Dragon the Revolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised to hear that\Nthe sons of those two are stepbrothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.60,0:21:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You two have filthy blood running through your veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if the others get away\Nas long as I can get the two of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.95,0:21:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.30,0:22:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is certainly a Vivre Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.24,0:22:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I haven't told you that this card
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,also tells you how much vital energy the owner has.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.21,0:22:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This card belongs to someone who you care for, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.02,0:22:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's my brother's!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold onto it, always.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:22:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That paper will lead us to one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace is pierced by Red Hound's fist\Nwhile protecting Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe and the Whitebeard Pirates try to save him,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but Ace, realizing he is about to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.03,0:23:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,finds the voice to convey his feelings\Nto his friends one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.80,0:23:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.27,0:23:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Looking for the Answer\NFire Fist Ace Dies on the Battlefield"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.04,0:23:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
